# MaNaReD Figma Design System Rules

How to translate the [MaNaReD Figma file](https://www.figma.com/design/y12p7ety9bAbG9Z7m5Bd6L/MaNaReD?node-id=31-80) into this RedwoodSDK + Astryx + Tailwind codebase.

Also see: [`DESIGN.md`](../../DESIGN.md) (full design reference), [`ui-stack.mdc`](./ui-stack.mdc) (RSC conventions), [`figma-to-prototype` skill](../skills/figma-to-prototype/SKILL.md) (workflow).

## Figma source of truth

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| File key | `y12p7ety9bAbG9Z7m5Bd6L` |
| UI Library page | node `31:80` |
| MCP | `.cursor/mcp.json` → `https://mcp.figma.com/mcp` |

The Figma file currently has one page (**UI Library**) with token documentation and icon symbols. Token names follow dot notation: `MaNaReD.{category}.{name}`.

Key Figma sections (node IDs for MCP):

| Section | Node | Pattern |
|---------|------|---------|
| Font | `32:5` | `MaNaReD.font.*` |
| Colour | `49:867` | `MaNaReD.colour.*` |
| Space | `81:470` | `MaNaReD.space.*` |
| Icons | `93:1469` | `icon/{name}` symbols |

