## 1. Token definitions

### Code (today)

Tokens live in **npm packages**, not repo files:

```css
/* src/app/styles.css — import order matters */
@layer reset, theme, base, astryx-base, astryx-theme, components, utilities;

@import "@astryxdesign/theme-neutral/theme.css";      /* --color-*, --spacing-*, --radius-* */
@import "@astryxdesign/core/tailwind-theme.css";       /* @theme inline → Tailwind utilities */
```

- **Format:** CSS custom properties (`--color-background-surface`, `--spacing-4`, `--radius-container`)
- **Transformation:** `tailwind-theme.css` maps vars → Tailwind v4 utilities (`bg-surface`, `text-primary`, `rounded-lg`, `p-4`)
- **Runtime theme:** `src/app/providers.tsx` wraps `<Theme theme={neutralTheme}>`
- **HTML marker:** `data-astryx-theme="neutral"` on `<html>` in `src/app/document.tsx`
- **No `tailwind.config.*`** — Tailwind v4 is CSS-first via `vite.config.ts` + `@tailwindcss/vite`

Discover token values locally:

```bash
vp run astryx -- docs tokens
vp run astryx -- docs theme
```

### Figma (MaNaReD custom system)

#### Typography (`MaNaReD.font.*`)

| Figma token | Value |
|-------------|-------|
| `MaNaReD.font.family.display` | Inter |
| `MaNaReD.font.family.content` | Inter |
| `MaNaReD.font.family.code` | Geist Mono |
| `MaNaReD.font.weight.default` | 400 |
| `MaNaReD.font.weight.semiBold` | 600 |
| `MaNaReD.font.weight.bold` | 700 |
| `MaNaReD.font.weight.black` | 900 |
| `MaNaReD.font.size.3xs` … `3xl` | 12px … 72px |

Map to Astryx: `<Heading level={n}>` / `<Text type="body" color="secondary">`. Do not hard-code px from Figma.

#### Colour (`MaNaReD.colour.*`)

Light-mode values from the UI Library (dark mode has parallel frames):

| Figma token | Light value | Code target |
|-------------|-------------|-------------|
| `MaNaReD.colour.BG.page` | `#E9F1F9` | `bg-body` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.BG.card` | `#FFFFFF` | `bg-surface` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.BG.sideBar` | `#F6FAFF` | `bg-[var(--color-background-sidebar)]` (custom var) |
| `MaNaReD.colour.text.primary` | `#2A2A2A` | `text-primary` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.text.secondary` | `#584F82` | `text-secondary` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.text.tertiary` | `#617990` | custom CSS var or `text-secondary` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.status.info` | BG `#465A6E` | `bg-info` / `Badge variant="info"` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.status.success` | BG `#6C8656` | `bg-success` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.status.warning` | BG `#AC8D5D` | `bg-warning` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.status.danger` | BG `#8E5963` | `bg-error` |
| `MaNaReD.colour.interactive.button` active | `#222133` | `<Button variant="primary">` |

**MaNaReD-only tokens** (no Astryx neutral equivalent — use custom CSS vars):

- **Entity colours:** `MaNaReD.colour.entity.{organism,bioactivity,compound,region}` — BG/border/text triplets for domain badges/chips
- **Interactive states:** button/chip/navItem/dropDown with active/hover/focus columns

Example entity token usage:

```tsx
<span className="rounded-md bg-[var(--color-entity-organism-bg)] px-2 py-1 text-[var(--color-entity-organism-text)]">
  Organism
</span>
```

#### Space (`MaNaReD.space.*`)

| Figma token | Value | Code target |
|-------------|-------|-------------|
| `MaNaReD.space.1` | 4px | `gap={1}`, `p-1` |
| `MaNaReD.space.2` | 8px | `gap={2}`, `p-2` |
| `MaNaReD.space.4` | 16px | `gap={4}`, `p-4` |
| `MaNaReD.space.6` | 24px | `gap={6}`, `p-6` |
| `MaNaReD.space.8` | 32px | `gap={8}`, `p-8` |
| `MaNaReD.space.10` | 40px | `gap={10}` |
| `MaNaReD.space.12` | 48px | `gap={12}` |

Prefer `VStack gap={n}` / `HStack gap={n}` over arbitrary Tailwind gap classes.

#### Shape (`MaNaReD.shape.*`)

| Figma token | Value | Code target |
|-------------|-------|-------------|
| `MaNaReD.shape.none` | 0px | `rounded-none` |
| `MaNaReD.shape.sm` | 4px | `rounded-sm` → `--radius-inner` |
| `MaNaReD.shape.md` | 8px | `rounded-md` → `--radius-element` |
| `MaNaReD.shape.lg` | 12px | `rounded-lg` → `--radius-container` |

### Bridging strategy

**Phase 1 (prototype):** Map Figma tokens to closest Astryx utilities; use `bg-[var(--color-*)]` for unmapped MaNaReD tokens.

**Phase 2 (brand fidelity):** Create a MaNaReD Astryx theme via `vp run astryx -- theme` / `defineTheme({ tokens: { ... } })`, replace `neutralTheme` in `providers.tsx`, add Inter + Geist Mono to `document.tsx` (CSP already allows `fonts.googleapis.com`).

