## 3. Frameworks and libraries

| Layer | Technology | Entry |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| Framework | React 19 + RedwoodSDK RSC | `src/worker.tsx`, `src/client.tsx` |
| UI system | Astryx `@astryxdesign/core` ^0.1.2 | `src/app/providers.tsx` |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 (no JS config) | `src/app/styles.css` |
| Build | Vite+ (`vp`) | `vite.config.ts`, `package.json` |
| Deploy | Cloudflare Workers + Wrangler | `wrangler.jsonc`, `vp run release` |
| Path alias | `@/*` → `./src/*` | `tsconfig.json` |

Route registration pattern:

```tsx
// src/worker.tsx
import { render, route } from "rwsdk/router";
import { Document } from "@/app/document";
import { Home } from "@/app/pages/home";

export default defineApp([
  setCommonHeaders(),
  render(Document, [route("/", Home)]),
]);
```

