## 4. Asset management

| Aspect | Current state | Figma MCP guidance |
|--------|---------------|-------------------|
| Static files | No `public/` folder; favicon referenced but missing | Use MCP `download_assets` / remote URLs from `get_design_context` |
| CSS | `import styles from "@/app/styles.css?url"` in Document | N/A |
| Cloudflare | `ASSETS` binding in wrangler, no directory configured | Add `public/` + wrangler assets dir when committing static files |
| CSP | `default-src 'self'` in `src/app/headers.ts` | External Figma asset URLs require CSP `img-src` update |

Stylesheet link pattern (RSC-friendly):

```tsx
// src/app/document.tsx
import styles from "@/app/styles.css?url";
// ...
<link rel="stylesheet" href={styles} />
```

**Rule:** Prefer Figma MCP-provided asset URLs for prototypes; only commit assets when needed for production.

