## 7. Project structure

```
src/
  worker.tsx              # Routes: render(Document, [route("/", Page)])
  client.tsx              # Hydration
  app/
    document.tsx          # HTML shell, stylesheet ?url link
    providers.tsx         # Astryx Theme (neutralTheme)
    styles.css            # Token + Tailwind layers
    headers.ts            # CSP / security middleware
    pages/                # Screens (Server Components)
      home.tsx
      home-form.tsx       # Client island
    shared/
      links.ts            # Typed router links
```

**Feature pattern:** one screen = one Server Component page + optional colocated client island; register new routes in `src/worker.tsx`.

Server + client island split:

```tsx
// home.tsx (Server Component)
import { HomeForm } from "./home-form";
<Card className="max-w-md"><HomeForm /></Card>

// home-form.tsx (Client island)
"use client";
export function HomeForm() {
  const [name, setName] = useState("");
  return (
    <VStack gap={3}>
      <TextInput label="Name" value={name} onChange={setName} />
      <Button label="Submit" variant="primary" onClick={() => {}} />
    </VStack>
  );
}
```

