## Figma MCP workflow

1. **Extract URL params:** fileKey `y12p7ety9bAbG9Z7m5Bd6L`, nodeId `31-80` → `31:80`
2. **`get_screenshot`** — visual target
3. **`get_design_context`** — structure, reference code (adapt to this stack; do not paste verbatim)
4. **`get_metadata`** — file tree when exploring; **`get_variable_defs`** on specific nodes for token values
5. **`vp run astryx -- build/search/component`** — map to Astryx
6. Implement in `src/app/pages/`, wire route in `worker.tsx`
7. Verify: `vp dev`, `vp check`

### Anti-patterns

- Whole-page `"use client"` for one form field
- Rebuilding buttons/inputs when Astryx has them
- Hard-coded px/hex from Figma instead of token mapping
- Ignoring Figma MCP and guessing layout
- Checking in Figma-exported assets when MCP provides URLs
- Overriding `--color-*` in `:root` — use `astryx theme` for brand changes
